-- Greece submits mid-term austerity plan to parliament
-- 
-- Thu Jun 9, 2011 1:32pm EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2011/06/09/us-greece-idUSTRE75853020110609

 

 ATHENS  (Reuters) - The Greek government on Thursday submitted to parliament the mid-term fiscal and privatization plan required by the EU and the IMF to put the country's finances back on track, the Finance Minister said. 

 "The cabinet approved the mid-term plan and submitted it to parliament," George Papaconstantinou told reporters. (Reporting by Lefteris Papadimas)